This comic book is about the world where history had been different, but the human flaws remained in place.

Alternative Russia 90th. After Civil War 1986-1988, the Empire collapsed. Petrograd is divided into two halves: Petropolis (Confederation) and the Red City (S.E.R.P.). A new wave of crime. Underground power in Petropolis captured by five gangster clans led by the person known as the Golokost. The new order, the corruption, the cult duplicity. But nothing can last forever. Three characters with different destiny, the purpose and sights try to break this vicious circle.

description:
In a rustic village outside of Manhattan, Misha and her fiance Daren seek an escape from the fast pace of the city. As they settle in, Misha becomes withdrawn, suffering from bad dreams and depression. When Daren brings his friends to the house, little does he know he is setting into motion events started hundreds of years ago with the original occupants of the house, the Willam Family. Not only did the ill-fated Willam family die in the house one cold winter, but the house has developed a history of female occupants committing suicide. The friends must solve the mystery of the house before the Willam Family ghosts pick them off one by one.
